channel.title: 2 Years tomorrow
channel.description:
Well, most everybody here probably has no clue who I am.. But.
Tomorrow will be the anniversary of the 2nd year that I have been here at MITB and MSCP. I haven't really posted in close to a year, but I have been trollin' these forums silently for a long, long time, way to long actually.
I didn't even know that I had been here for 2 years, I checked my profile out and I noticed that I registered December 20th of 2006.
I can still remember my first major topic that I posted over on MSCP, it was for my private server "JGHS Scape". I look back on my time at this site and I can recall some great stuff, some great people, hilarious topics, some horrible moderators, some great ones. :( ;)
I just wanted to post this to say thank's to Mopar for giving me a great 2 years of shit to do on the Internet, and for giving me some great ass comebacks to use at school. I make "nerd" comebacks more popular everyday in my school, so thanks for that also :P
Later everyone ;)
